high_descs: Walk past the shelves, through the door next to them and into the kitchen to the far end of the diningtable.
Pick up the potato that is on the plate on the kitchen table.
Walk out of the kitchen, through the living room and into the bathroom to the sink.
Place the potato in the sink to wash it with water then retrieve it.
Walk out of the bathroom, through the living room, and into the kitchen over to the fridge.
Place the potato into the fridge on the first large shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Wash a potato in the bathroom sink to put in the fridge.

high_descs: Go into the left door of the two doors on your right, and go to the diningtable.
Pick up the potato off of the table.
Leave the room go straight to the wall and take a left, into the bathroom and go to the sink.
Rinse off the potato in the sink and then take it out of the sink.
Leave the bathroom take a right and go into the door on the left straight ahead.
Put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a Potato and put it in the Fridge.
